apps/3199380/extras/2ccd77e30ef226463d9b7c17cd1aef24.webp?t=1767614444\" width=600 height=44 /></span>Your fortune and freedom are at stake! Customize your character to unlock gameplay features, and become the ultimate highwaywoman! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199380/extras/4584578cc04dfc6a694414e24a893f18.webp?t=1767614444\" width=600 height=11 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199380/extras/cddfdc97c1188924ea10001032221583.webp?t=1767614444\" width=600 height=44 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Smooth, satisfying solitaire gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Disguise Lady Cornelia in spectacular costumes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Sumptuous art and dramatic adventure story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Prequel to Regency Solitaire (in 1770s England)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Over 150 unique levels spread over 22 chapters </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Unlock dozens of exciting gameplay upgrades.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Relaxed, Normal and Hard modes. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Specially-composed, classical music.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Set backgrounds as Desktop Wallpaper.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199380/extras/4679ee45d8fbc44320bb707fc8451ab8.avif?t=1767614444\" width=620 height=204 /></span></p>",
